ough of them are looking for groups.<br>
<br>
One thing you super Magicians out there need to realize.  You can always replace damage from a Magician with another class.  So dont make it seem like the show would not go on without you.<br>
<br>
Also, this is not being negative,,,its being realistic.  Do people want us in groups...yes.  But pretty much after they make sure they have a slower and healer.  We are wanted after that.  Unless it is a all pet group.  But still the preference is Slower, Healer, Tank.  <br>
