What I've read on this board so far and what I've experienced myself is  that people don't know how much damage a mage can do.  They never see how much damage the pet is doing, and it has been lauded that Wizards are the best nukers in the game.  In any group I've ever been in by the time I leave everybody there knows that the mage is preferable to the wiz.  My pet can take the agro off of the tank and my nukes are almost as good as any wizzies.<br>
What I've read on here about full caster groups is so true.  They are by far the most fun and result in more kills.  The best group I've been in was three mages a cleric and a necro.  Casters always appreciate the fact that we need mana to fight.  I've been in groups where the tank just keeps pulling despite the OOM cries from everybody including the healers.  Thats when the casters discreetly agree that it would be best if we all gated away on our deaf tank friend.<br>
