<br>
Stormhammer is a unique situation where the population is small, and quite frankly, there aren't a ton of people around lower than myself that are LFG (though this is more of a server balancing problem, not a game balance problem.)<br>
<br>
While this option worked fairly well in my younger days when there were more mid-levels on the server, I only did it for fun, as back then, I could usually get better xp solo.<br>
<br>
I still find that equation to be true for my level, though PoP solo isn't really an option outside of PoJ prisoners/rats.<br>
<br>
Xp rates if pulls are pretty consistent:<br>
<br>
PoP Solo &gt; PoP Groups &gt; Old world Solo Xp &gt; Non-PoP Groups<br>
<br>
For your average mage that decides to go to 65, three of these options go away according to most accounts. Those who say otherwise tend to have gear / AA levels i couldn't dream of having, especially anytime soon. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381929"> Naladini </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
